Battera::

She looked at Vulios. "I'm worried about CyberShark. You stay here 
and I'll go find him."

She transformed into bat mode and flew out of the cave. She had a 
tough time following his signature, but she found it and followed it.

It took her flying bast the old location of the Allience base. She 
looked down,"Where did it go? It was there last time I looked."

She kept flying out. She opened her link to him,"CyberShark, where 
are you? It's Battera, please come in."
